1
00:00:06,640 --> 00:00:10,039
You've been staring at the screen for a long time.

2
00:00:10,280 --> 00:00:11,839
Don't just watch.

3
00:00:12,240 --> 00:00:15,159
Subscribe, coin, and like.

4
00:00:15,480 --> 00:00:17,839
I demand your one-click triple combo.

5
00:00:20,560 --> 00:00:22,599
I want it now.

6
00:00:41,000 --> 00:00:43,519
Granny, Grandpa, and Ancestor...

7
00:00:43,800 --> 00:00:45,279
have all gone to Carefree Village.

8
00:00:54,240 --> 00:00:55,759
Old Master, half a year without seeing you—

9
00:00:55,840 --> 00:00:57,159
so you went *there*.

10
00:00:59,240 --> 00:01:01,199
Where is Carefree Village?

11
00:01:03,160 --> 00:01:04,160
Mu'er.

12
00:01:04,880 --> 00:01:05,999
Got any food?

13
00:01:06,240 --> 00:01:07,719
I've been starving for days.

14
00:01:08,400 --> 00:01:09,799
Deafy Grandpa.

15
00:01:09,880 --> 00:01:10,919
You're back.

16
00:01:11,200 --> 00:01:12,359
Food will be ready shortly.

17
00:02:12,240 --> 00:02:13,240
Mu'er's culinary skills...

18
00:02:13,280 --> 00:02:16,119
are indistinguishable from the head chefs in Yan Kang's capital taverns.

19
00:02:20,040 --> 00:02:22,119
Old Master, where have you been these days?

20
00:02:25,600 --> 00:02:27,039
Went to Yan Kang to find the Mute.

21
00:02:27,040 --> 00:02:28,519
Travel funds ran out.

22
00:02:28,840 --> 00:02:29,959
Had to sell paintings.

23
00:02:30,920 --> 00:02:32,839
People lack the virtue of the ancients.

24
00:02:32,840 --> 00:02:34,439
Couldn't sell a single one.

25
00:02:35,480 --> 00:02:37,039
Was truly starving,

26
00:02:37,120 --> 00:02:38,679
met Old Lady Si,

27
00:02:38,880 --> 00:02:40,279
she gave me some coins,

28
00:02:40,640 --> 00:02:42,559
and mocked me for a good while.

29
00:02:44,440 --> 00:02:46,359
Don't tell the Medicine Master about this.

30
00:02:46,920 --> 00:02:50,439
That guy always laughs that my paintings don't sell as fast as his medicines.

31
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:53,439
Times are troubled now,

32
00:02:53,840 --> 00:02:55,279
so no one buys paintings to collect.

33
00:02:56,040 --> 00:02:57,199
Next time you're short on cash,

34
00:02:57,240 --> 00:02:58,399
just sell them to the National Preceptor's Manor.

35
00:02:58,920 --> 00:03:01,839
The Yan Kang National Preceptor would surely pay a high price.

36
00:03:02,960 --> 00:03:06,439
I wiped out tens of thousands of his troops last time.

37
00:03:07,200 --> 00:03:09,039
Going to his house to sell paintings...

38
00:03:09,080 --> 00:03:11,239
He'll definitely use *Orthodoxy* on me.

39
00:03:11,360 --> 00:03:12,759
I can't beat him.

40
00:03:14,120 --> 00:03:15,159
Come find me at the Academy.

41
00:03:16,040 --> 00:03:17,439
However many paintings you bring, I'll buy them all.

42
00:03:18,040 --> 00:03:19,839
Are there other paintings in the study?

43
00:03:20,440 --> 00:03:21,440
All burned.

44
00:03:24,720 --> 00:03:25,839
What about the others?

45
00:03:32,040 --> 00:03:33,439
Terrible handwriting.

46
00:03:34,480 --> 00:03:35,999
I'll go find them tomorrow.

47
00:03:39,920 --> 00:03:41,079
What is this?

48
00:03:42,040 --> 00:03:42,639
I am...

49
00:03:42,640 --> 00:03:43,759
Ugly looking.

50
00:03:46,360 --> 00:03:47,360
You!

51
00:03:49,960 --> 00:03:52,039
Your elders have even less manners than you.

52
00:03:52,480 --> 00:03:53,480
Demon King.

53
00:03:53,840 --> 00:03:55,199
Deafy Grandpa can't hear.

54
00:03:55,680 --> 00:03:57,959
He just heard what you said clearly.

55
00:03:58,920 --> 00:04:00,279
Sometimes he can hear,

56
00:04:00,600 --> 00:04:01,600
sometimes he can't.

57
00:04:01,920 --> 00:04:03,119
I see.

58
00:04:08,320 --> 00:04:09,320
One more thing.

59
00:04:09,840 --> 00:04:11,679
Demon King, don't run around at night.

60
00:04:12,160 --> 00:04:13,719
The darkness is very dangerous.

61
00:04:15,720 --> 00:04:18,239
This brat dares not enter the darkness—

62
00:04:18,240 --> 00:04:20,319
Perfect timing for my escape.

63
00:04:20,960 --> 00:04:22,839
Once I enter the darkness,

64
00:04:22,840 --> 00:04:24,359
I'll preside over the Grand Sacrifice,

65
00:04:24,640 --> 00:04:26,079
and summon my true body

66
00:04:26,080 --> 00:04:27,959
to descend upon this world.

67
00:04:51,960 --> 00:04:54,759
Now is the perfect time to leave.

68
00:05:09,960 --> 00:05:11,159
This darkness...

69
00:05:11,280 --> 00:05:14,239
It's different from the one in the Capital Sky World.

70
00:05:27,240 --> 00:05:29,439
Constant Mo Corpse Chicken Granny Emperor...

71
00:05:32,640 --> 00:05:35,079
Bu Na He Chicken Granny Sac...

72
00:05:42,640 --> 00:05:43,640
What are you doing?

73
00:05:44,240 --> 00:05:45,759
Why are you speaking Demon Tongue?

74
00:05:47,120 --> 00:05:48,639
If there is a next time,

75
00:05:49,160 --> 00:05:50,160
I will certainly not spare you lightly.

76
00:05:50,800 --> 00:05:52,559
This old timer's ears are sharp.

77
00:05:52,800 --> 00:05:53,800
Wait.

78
00:05:53,960 --> 00:05:55,799
Isn't he supposed to be deaf?

79
00:06:06,440 --> 00:06:07,239
Mu'er.

80
00:06:07,440 --> 00:06:09,279
I'm going out to find the Village Chief and the others.

81
00:06:10,400 --> 00:06:12,719
You and Big Dog watch the village.

82
00:06:13,320 --> 00:06:14,839
I am not a dog.

83
00:06:15,920 --> 00:06:17,999
I am the Auspicious Beast, half-dragon, half-qilin.

84
00:06:25,880 --> 00:06:26,880
Deafy Master.

85
00:06:26,960 --> 00:06:29,399
Help keep an eye on my Master.

86
00:06:33,360 --> 00:06:34,639
Did he hear me or not?

87
00:06:37,040 --> 00:06:38,239
He probably heard.

88
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:44,399
Wonder how Big Guy is doing lately.

89
00:06:45,160 --> 00:06:47,039
I organized some techniques from the Book Pavilion.

90
00:06:47,600 --> 00:06:48,959
They should suit his cultivation well.

91
00:06:49,720 --> 00:06:51,639
I told you not to run around.

92
00:06:53,640 --> 00:06:55,199
Constant Mo Corpse Chicken Granny Emperor...

93
00:06:58,440 --> 00:06:59,959
This brat knows too.

94
00:07:01,840 --> 00:07:02,840
Strange.

95
00:07:03,360 --> 00:07:05,079
Why are Big Guy and Dragon Elephant gone?

96
00:07:05,103 --> 00:07:23,603
(Watch the Latest Donghua Episodes: www.h-donghua.xyz)

97
00:07:24,280 --> 00:07:26,239
Wearing iron shoes everywhere in vain,

98
00:07:26,320 --> 00:07:28,159
found without effort.

99
00:07:30,400 --> 00:07:33,319
Never expected to meet the Heavenly Demon Cult Leader here.

100
00:07:33,640 --> 00:07:34,839
Step aside.

101
00:07:35,400 --> 00:07:37,959
Demon Head, you are full of cunning schemes.

102
00:07:38,120 --> 00:07:39,639
Releasing the Root Demon to scatter us,

103
00:07:39,640 --> 00:07:41,119
causing the death of several comrades.

104
00:07:41,520 --> 00:07:43,079
Your sins are heavy.

105
00:07:44,000 --> 00:07:46,119
That Root Demon has already been suppressed by the Holy Church.

106
00:07:46,560 --> 00:07:47,999
If not for you letting it go,

107
00:07:48,200 --> 00:07:49,999
how would it have had the chance to harm again?

108
00:07:51,040 --> 00:07:54,719
If not for you, Demon Head, making the Root Demon disguise itself to deceive us,

109
00:07:54,800 --> 00:07:57,759
how could such a tragic event have occurred?

110
00:07:59,560 --> 00:08:02,439
Zen Master, your Heart Demon is deep indeed.

111
00:08:03,240 --> 00:08:06,239
Demon Head, let me send you on your way.

112
00:08:08,040 --> 00:08:09,999
Perfect timing to test my skills on you.

113
00:08:10,160 --> 00:08:12,959
Trying out my perfected Five-Yao Divinization form.

114
00:08:40,760 --> 00:08:42,439
I am not one who enjoys killing.

115
00:08:42,600 --> 00:08:44,799
I have long since refined my evil thoughts into Zen beads.

116
00:08:46,640 --> 00:08:48,639
Now, employing thunderous means

117
00:08:49,240 --> 00:08:51,039
to rid the world of a scourge.

118
00:08:51,440 --> 00:08:52,440
Come, good.

119
00:08:56,440 --> 00:08:58,039
Such intense Metal Qi.

120
00:09:04,120 --> 00:09:06,119
Truly a demonic path technique.

121
00:09:20,360 --> 00:09:22,719
Using evil thoughts to forcefully boost strength—

122
00:09:22,800 --> 00:09:24,279
Is this your Zen heart?

123
00:09:25,080 --> 00:09:26,879
Demon Head, I will not listen to your demonic words.

124
00:09:27,160 --> 00:09:29,079
Void Meditation Seal! Go!

125
00:09:36,600 --> 00:09:37,919
If there is a next life,

126
00:09:38,040 --> 00:09:40,239
be reborn as a good person.

127
00:10:09,280 --> 00:10:11,079
Vajra Invincible!

128
00:10:14,840 --> 00:10:17,799
Spawn of evil, die!

129
00:10:52,680 --> 00:10:53,999
It ends here.

130
00:10:54,000 --> 00:10:55,000
It ends here.

131
00:11:11,000 --> 00:11:12,359
A combat expert of the Six Harmonies Realm.

132
00:11:12,760 --> 00:11:14,039
Not to be underestimated.

133
00:11:20,440 --> 00:11:21,639
Young Master,

134
00:11:22,720 --> 00:11:23,919
Young Master, you are injured!

135
00:11:50,240 --> 00:11:51,839
The venomous insect from Sanqi Fortress—

136
00:11:52,360 --> 00:11:53,599
It is that woman.

137
00:11:53,960 --> 00:11:55,159
She is already at the Seven Stars Realm.

138
00:11:55,280 --> 00:11:56,519
Stronger than Ban Chi.

139
00:11:58,960 --> 00:12:01,719
That insect flew from the banks of the Yong River.

140
00:12:02,240 --> 00:12:04,559
We can ambush her there.

141
00:12:33,400 --> 00:12:33,999
Young Master.

142
00:12:34,160 --> 00:12:35,160
What are you doing?

143
00:12:35,360 --> 00:12:36,360
Fighting.

144
00:12:37,400 --> 00:12:38,839
Fighting again?

145
00:13:00,040 --> 00:13:02,159
The Fish Monsters of the Yong River are also Five-Yao Realm.

146
00:13:02,600 --> 00:13:05,639
Yet before the venomous insect she raised, they were crushed instantly.

147
00:13:06,760 --> 00:13:07,999
Heavenly Demon Cult Leader.

148
00:13:17,640 --> 00:13:19,439
How should I address the lady from Sanqi Fortress?

149
00:13:22,960 --> 00:13:24,599
The Cult Leader holds high authority,

150
00:13:24,960 --> 00:13:26,839
supreme under heaven, yet you are so polite to your enemy?

151
00:13:27,320 --> 00:13:29,239
Calling me 'Big Sister'.

152
00:13:29,640 --> 00:13:30,999
Within the Great Ruins, I am not the Heavenly Demon Cult Leader.

153
00:13:31,960 --> 00:13:34,159
I am just an ordinary child from the Crippled Old Village.

154
00:13:35,040 --> 00:13:37,239
I also ask you to let go of grudges,

155
00:13:38,240 --> 00:13:39,639
leave the Great Ruins,

156
00:13:39,920 --> 00:13:40,920
go back for the New Year,

157
00:13:41,400 --> 00:13:42,439
and live well.

158
00:13:43,040 --> 00:13:44,399
The New Year...

159
00:13:47,160 --> 00:13:48,239
Yes.

160
00:13:49,040 --> 00:13:50,079
Everyone should go home for the New Year.

161
00:13:50,680 --> 00:13:52,959
It is just that...

162
00:13:53,840 --> 00:13:54,840
It is just that...

163
00:13:54,960 --> 00:13:57,319
My home was already reduced to ashes.

164
00:13:57,640 --> 00:14:00,239
Destroyed by you and the Yan Kang National Preceptor.

165
00:14:01,040 --> 00:14:02,759
My home was in Sanqi Fortress.

166
00:14:02,760 --> 00:14:04,439
My Ancestral Master was Lord Tian.

167
00:14:04,440 --> 00:14:06,439
My beloved master was Princess Tian You.

168
00:14:07,240 --> 00:14:08,719
In the Battle of Great Xiang City,

169
00:14:09,320 --> 00:14:12,199
the Heavenly Demon Cult delivered the Yan Kang army to the city,

170
00:14:13,040 --> 00:14:15,799
killing countless of my senior brothers and sisters.

171
00:14:16,160 --> 00:14:17,839
My master shielded me,

172
00:14:17,840 --> 00:14:19,999
and died at the hands of the Duke of Wei.

173
00:14:20,360 --> 00:14:22,359
I sneaked back to Sanqi Fortress,

174
00:14:22,960 --> 00:14:25,279
only to find my family labeled as rebels,

175
00:14:25,600 --> 00:14:27,079
their heads displayed in public.

176
00:14:28,160 --> 00:14:30,839
In this lifetime, I can never celebrate the New Year again.

177
00:14:31,360 --> 00:14:34,079
I have no home left to return to.

178
00:14:34,800 --> 00:14:37,719
Cult Leader, should I kill you or not?

179
00:14:38,360 --> 00:14:39,360
I should.

180
00:14:39,760 --> 00:14:41,719
But when you rebelled, you should have considered

181
00:14:42,360 --> 00:14:43,399
what fate

182
00:14:44,680 --> 00:14:46,599
would befall your family upon failure.

183
00:14:49,840 --> 00:14:53,519
Justice always requires some to risk their lives to uphold it.

184
00:14:53,840 --> 00:14:56,199
Otherwise, where would justice exist under heaven?

185
00:14:56,760 --> 00:14:57,760
Cult Leader,

186
00:14:57,840 --> 00:14:59,279
say no more.

187
00:14:59,640 --> 00:15:02,279
This concubine is here to send you on your way.

188
00:15:09,280 --> 00:15:10,879
Different paths lead to no cooperation.

189
00:15:59,440 --> 00:16:00,839
Dragon-Horned Lad did not come.

190
00:16:01,040 --> 00:16:02,439
Got lost?

191
00:16:02,440 --> 00:16:04,039
Or got taken out on the way?

192
00:16:04,240 --> 00:16:06,599
Or perhaps she is nearby...

193
00:16:12,760 --> 00:16:14,439
Heavenly Demon Cult Leader.

194
00:16:14,680 --> 00:16:16,439
Killing a beauty—

195
00:16:16,720 --> 00:16:18,919
you must be in quite a good mood.

196
00:16:19,680 --> 00:16:21,239
The Deaf One ran away too.

197
00:16:21,320 --> 00:16:22,639
Untie me.

198
00:16:23,440 --> 00:16:24,719
Hurry up, hurry up.

199
00:16:25,320 --> 00:16:26,559
I can't move, it's uncomfortable.

200
00:16:27,120 --> 00:16:28,120
Quick, quick.

201
00:16:30,480 --> 00:16:31,559
What are you doing?

202
00:16:32,760 --> 00:16:33,959
Are you crazy?

203
00:16:37,440 --> 00:16:38,440
Stop!

204
00:16:39,360 --> 00:16:40,360
Don't hit!

205
00:17:00,040 --> 00:17:01,639
Smelly brat!

206
00:17:01,640 --> 00:17:04,159
How have I offended you this time?

207
00:17:07,373 --> 00:17:16,073
[Taibai Star Lord — Divine Manifestation: The Metal deity of the Five Luminaries, ruler of all metal energy. In this form, one draws in metal power, turning vital energy into steel— making weapons sharper and stronger.]

208
00:17:16,097 --> 00:17:23,997
[Jupiter Star Lord — Divine Manifestation: The Wood deity of the Five Luminaries, ruler of life and growth. In this form, vital energy becomes wood energy—capable of healing wounds and controlling plants in battle.]

209
00:17:24,021 --> 00:17:34,021
[Water Star Lord — Divine Manifestation: The Water deity of the Five Luminaries, nourishing all things through water. In this form, vital energy becomes water energy— and all abilities take on the power of water.]

210
00:17:34,045 --> 00:17:54,545
FANSUB: H-DONGHUA™

